SUMMARY:Birding Tour at Hart-Miller Island on May 21\, 2026
DESCRIPTION:Feast your eyes on some of the most extraordinary birds that Maryland has to offer.  \nThe Maryland Port Administration is pleased to welcome the general public to participate in an upcoming birding tour. This birding experience is free to the public. \nPlease note the Birding Tour Details and Safety Information below before registering. Questions can be directed to the birding tour leader at Maryland Ports Birding [birdingtours@menv.com]. \nLottery Entrance Deadline: May 6\, at 11:59 pm\nLottery Selections Announced: May 7\, 2026\nEvent Date: May 21\, 2026 (if selected\, please arrive by 8:45am)\nEvent Location 2024A Riverview Road\, Essex\, MD 21221 Parking: Take a right into the lot\, and park in the gravel area. Please wait by the shed until an MES staff member meets you. \n\n                \n                        \n                            Hart-Miller Island Birding – May 21\, 2026\n                             \n                         \n \n                        Primary Entrant: Name(Required)\n                            \n                            \n                                                    First\n                                                    \n                                                \n                            \n                            \n                                                            Last\n                                                            \n                                                        \n                            \n                        Email(Required)\n                                \n                                    Enter Email\n                                    \n                                \n                                \n                                    Confirm Email\n                                    \n                                \n                                \n                            Main PhoneAre you 18 years or older?(Required)If you are not 18\, you can still join this tour but need someone over 18 to both register and accompany you. \n								\n								Yes\n							Is this the first MPA birding tour that you or any of the additional participants in your group have attended?(Required)\n			\n					\n					Yes\n			\n			\n					\n					No\n			Do you or the additional participant/s of your group need a Spanish language interpreter?(Required)\n			\n					\n					Yes\n			\n			\n					\n					No\n			I will read and follow the safety guidelines including that tours are led on unpaved surfaces and that I will wear closed-toe shoes?(Required)Read guidelines
URL:https://maryland-dmmp.com/event/birding-tour-at-hart-miller-island-on-may-21-2026/
LOCATION:Hart-Miller Island\, 2024A Riverview Rd\, Essex\, MD\, 21221\, United States
CATEGORIES:Birding Tours
END:VEVENT
